videos.headline: Highlight: No. 5 Texas defeats UTRGV, extends win streak to six
videos.description: Kyla Oldacre scores 21 points in 24 minutes of playing time while Madison Booker tallies a season-high seven assists to secure a 94-35 win for the Longhorns vs. the Vaqueros.
